d a fishing boats-filled harbor. Bring your camera because the town is very picturesque. It also is a great place to sit in the sun and enjoy some pastries. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/ferragudo\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Ferragudo<\/a> is a 40-minute drive east of Lagos.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also visit:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/portugal\/sintra-portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The fairytale palaces and castles of Sintra<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104902\/portugese-fishing-village-Ferragudo-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-49061 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104902\/portugese-fishing-village-Ferragudo-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104902\/portugese-fishing-village-Ferragudo-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104902\/portugese-fishing-village-Ferragudo-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104902\/portugese-fishing-village-Ferragudo-400x