oeiro<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The picture-perfect village named Carvoeiro lies 10 minutes away from Ferragudo. Carvoeiro&#x2019;s small beach and its traditional houses are tucked away in between two towering cliffs. <br>Different from Ferragudo, Carvoeiro is very lively with a lot of good restaurants and shops. <strong>Tip:<\/strong> Get a fantastic lunch at <a href=\"https:\/\/goo.gl\/maps\/td3mKCxYVEkANSop6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener nofollow\">Organic<\/a>. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104832\/algarve-portugal-village-Carvoeiro-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"algarve portugal village Carvoeiro\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"algarve portugal village Carvoeiro\" class=\"wp-image-49086 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104832\/algarve-portugal-village-Carvoeiro-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104832\/algarve-portugal-village-Carvoeiro-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104832\/algarve-portugal-village-Carvoeiro-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104832\/algarve-portugal-village-Carvoeiro-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104832\/algarve-portugal-village-Carvoeiro-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104832\/algarve-portugal-village-Carvoeiro-1025x1536.jpg 1025w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104832\/algarve-portugal-village-Carvoeiro-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\