t road takes you along 10 different viewpoints indicated by letters ranging from A to J. The road is only accessible by regular cars and not allowed to access with a motorhome. We&#x2019;ve added the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/shop\/google-maps\/portugal\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">exact loop to our Google Maps Locations<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels\">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/algarve-hotels-all\/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Here are all your hotel options in Algarve.<\/a><\/p>\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104807\/algarve-portugal-sunset-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"algarve portugal sunset\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"algarve portugal sunset\" class=\"wp-image-49104 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104807\/algarve-portugal-sunset-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104807\/algarve-portugal-sunset-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104807\/algarve-portugal-sunset-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104807\/algarve-portugal-sunset-400x600.jpg 